				<p class="text-din-medium privacy_section_header">Core Values</p>

				<li class="text-din terms_li_no_bullet" style="padding-bottom: 8px;">Non-partisan: We are independent and do not support or oppose a particular political party or MP.</li>
				<li class="text-din terms_li_no_bullet" style="padding-bottom: 8px;">Transparent: Provide clear sources for our summaries and the process we use.</li>
				<li class="text-din terms_li_no_bullet">Accurate: All our content is based on Westminister summaries and bill texts.</li>


				<p class="text-din-medium privacy_section_header" style="padding-bottom: 8px;">We Provide</p>

				<li class="text-din terms_li_no_bullet text-din-medium list_style_none">Three defined services for the public:</li>

